OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FA "Hillsborough Law" will be
OL,7,Fintroduced in Parliament before the
OL,8,Fnext anniversary of the football
OL,9,Fstadium tragedy, Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,10,Fto promise.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister will also announce
OL,13,Fthat work has begun to recruit a new
OL,14,Findependent public advocate to
OL,15,Frepresent victims of disasters.
