OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough Law will introduce a
OL,7,Flegal duty of candour on public
OL,8,Fbodies, with the potential for
OL,9,Fcriminal sanctions for officials or
OL,10,Forganisations which mislead or
OL,11,Fobstruct investigations.
OL,13,FCampaigners have been calling for new
OL,14,Flegislation to prevent the experiences
OL,15,Fof families of the 97 Liverpool fans
OL,16,Fwho were killed in the 1989 disaster
OL,17,Fhappening again, and to help victims
OL,18,Fof other scandals to get justice.
