OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FSpeaking in Liverpool at the Labour
OL,7,FParty conference, Sir Keir will say he
OL,8,Fis meeting a commitment he made two
OL,9,Fyears ago to change the law if he
OL,10,Fbecame prime minister.
OL,12,F"For many people in this city, the
OL,13,Fspeech they may remember was the one
OL,14,Fhere, two years ago.
OL,16,F"Because that was when I promised, on
OL,17,Fthis stage, that if I ever had the
OL,18,Fprivilege to serve our country as
OL,19,Fprime minister, one of my first acts
OL,20,Fwould be to bring in a Hillsborough
OL,21,FLaw ` a duty of candour.
