OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,F"A law for Liverpool. A law for the
OL,7,F97. A law that people should never
OL,8,Fhave needed to fight so hard to get.
OL,9,FBut that will be delivered by this
OL,10,FLabour Government."
OL,12,FHe will add: "Today I can confirm that
OL,13,Fthe duty of candour will apply to
OL,14,Fpublic authorities and public
OL,15,Fservants, that Bill will include
OL,16,Fcriminal sanctions, and that the
OL,17,FHillsborough Law will be introduced to
OL,18,FParliament before the next anniversary
OL,19,Fin April."
