OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FThe duty of candour will be supported
OL,7,Fby a code of ethics for public bodies
OL,8,Fand authorities to address the wider
OL,9,Fculture of defensiveness seen in the
OL,10,Fwake of public disasters such as
OL,11,FHillsborough and Grenfell, and public
OL,12,Fscandals including infected blood, the
OL,13,FPost Office Horizon IT system and
OL,14,FWindrush.
