OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FThe change sees the Government taking
OL,7,Fforward recommendations made by Bishop
OL,8,FJames Jones in his 2017 report into
OL,9,Fthe experience of the Hillsborough
OL,10,Ffamilies in the years following the
OL,11,Fcrush which resulted in the death of
OL,12,FLiverpool supporters at the stadium in
OL,13,FSheffield.
OL,15,FAlongside the promised law, the
OL,16,FGovernment has begun the process of
OL,17,Frecruiting the first independent
OL,18,Fpublic advocate (IPA).
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
