OL,3,CHillsborough Law 'will be introduced
OL,4,Cby anniversary of disaster'
OL,6,FThe IPA will be sent to the scene of
OL,7,Fany future public disaster, playing a
OL,8,Fpivotal role in ensuring victims,
OL,9,Fsurvivors, and bereaved families get
OL,10,Fthe information and support they need.
OL,12,FThe advocate is expected to be in post
OL,13,Fby next summer and will inform victims
OL,14,Fabout sources of support, advice and
OL,15,Fservices available to them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
